#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1204
msgid ""
"Responses include a <code>429 Too Many Requests</code> with a <code>Retry-"
"After</code> header indicating seconds until the next request is allowed."
msgstr ""
"Las respuestas incluyen un <code>429 Too Many Requests</code> con un "
"encabezado <code>Retry-After</code> indicando segundos hasta que se permita "
"la siguiente solicitud."

#: app/templates/partner/api_docs.html:1207
msgid ""
"<strong>Integrity mode:</strong> Some discussions have stricter vote rate "
"limits enabled for integrity protection. The embed handles this "
"transparently &mdash; users see a &ldquo;please slow down&rdquo; message."
msgstr ""
