#: app/templates/partner/portal/getting_started.html:284
msgid ""
"Set up webhook callbacks in the dashboard to avoid polling and keep Observer"
" systems in sync. Verify <code>X-SocietySpeaks-Signature</code> on your "
"receiver and treat <code>X-SocietySpeaks-Event-Id</code> as idempotent."
msgstr ""
"Configura callbacks de webhook en el dashboard para evitar sondeos y "
"mantener los sistemas Observer sincronizados. Verifica "
"<code>X-SocietySpeaks-Signature</code> en tu receptor y trata "
"<code>X-SocietySpeaks-Event-Id</code> como idempotente."

